Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.80,0:01:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山是分了七層\N由神僊居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.27,0:01:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了打倒支配這座山的\N邪惡帝皇多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.47,0:01:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一邊在各界層\N與多惡達的魔神戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.17,0:01:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一邊向第七界層進發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.98,0:01:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了得到\N能令龍神丸重生的復活聖水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.35,0:01:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們上了第五界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.95,0:01:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然全靠空神丸\N令我得到了復活聖水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.12,0:01:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但空神丸卻被布力奇2號\N破壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.86,0:02:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是重生了的龍神丸\N和空神丸的靈魂合了體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.96,0:02:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力量變得更強成為了龍王丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.46,0:02:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也會是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.17,0:02:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十三話\N等很久了!幻神丸的正體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.21,0:02:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山的彩虹已恢復了一半\N令我鬆了一大口氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.65,0:02:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡他們也好像上了第五界層\N真是可喜可賀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.80,0:02:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.39,0:02:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!老公公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.90,0:02:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一段時間不見你\N你去了哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.50,0:02:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去買糰子回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.31,0:02:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是幻龍齊很喜歡的草糰子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.80,0:03:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來幻龍齊說要\N打倒多惡達而離開這條村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.52,0:03:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正是五年前的今日呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.22,0:03:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親加油…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.46,0:03:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底現在在哪裏幹什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.57,0:03:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣\N等渡和火美子打倒了多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.24,0:03:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我便再沒有其他渴求了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.65,0:03:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呢,火美子,你要和渡\N一起完成你父親的心願啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安全著地,超人死光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真無論何時也這麼精神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.47,0:03:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明空氣這麼污濁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是忍者所以沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.61,0:04:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?做忍者真方便呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像明白又好像不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.95,0:04:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來間中會出來救我們\N那像忍者的魔神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.65,0:04:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是什麼人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部使用巨型飛鏢的傢伙嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.16,0:04:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像不是敵人\N是誰駕駛的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.53,0:04:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是河啊,我很口渴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個白癡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.55,0:04:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,懶惰的人?  (近音)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.42,0:04:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.09,0:04:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然推開人不是很危險嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.20,0:04:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼也不知道\N你們是外面的人吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.76,0:04:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看清楚好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.80,0:04:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.67,0:05:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害!厲害!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.61,0:05:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這條依達羅村\N以前有水果村之稱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.55,0:05:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山最清澈的水\N也流進村中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.22,0:05:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是有一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.52,0:05:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那條有如生命重要\N的河被污染了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.56,0:05:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住在這第五界層的\N煙霧大人的部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.66,0:05:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把這條河川整個污染了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,村內的田也枯乾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.85,0:05:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,河也變得住不了人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.66,0:05:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!你們有聽人說話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.83,0:05:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然在聽啊,是吧?師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.56,0:06:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.50,0:06:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吧,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.35,0:06:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的進度是120%\N今天的污染也很成功呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這氣味真令人受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.40,0:06:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們好像來了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.24,0:06:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏便是萬人沼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.10,0:06:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣味真難嗅呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.81,0:06:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像糞便一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.31,0:06:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有花開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.25,0:06:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的\N那傢伙到底是什麼構造的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.29,0:07:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好怪的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.07,0:07:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.81,0:07:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,火美子的臉變得很紅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.31,0:07:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像沒有發燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.80,0:07:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅\N你用我的額頭探熱怎知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.39,0:07:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呢,這邊才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱!不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是很高燒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.86,0:07:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子!火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.53,0:07:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎辦好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.40,0:07:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣也好,這裏到處是陷阱\N回婆婆處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.71,0:07:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一作戰成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.92,0:08:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中了怪花的毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.36,0:08:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用生長在萬人沼的萬人草\N可以救她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.83,0:08:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的?太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,你等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.93,0:08:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去萬人沼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去也沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.80,0:08:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.84,0:08:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那處沒有架橋\N普通的船又會被溶掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.51,0:08:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然也不能游去\N誰也去不了上游
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.55,0:08:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎會的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.35,0:08:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,怎辦好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.26,0:08:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣也沒法子嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.36,0:08:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有一個方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.49,0:08:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如用村頭那棵\N不可思議樹的木造成的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.66,0:08:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該可以渡過沼澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可思議樹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.90,0:08:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不可思議的樹幹\N被沼澤的水灑過也沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.54,0:09:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼用這棵樹造船\N便可以了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.71,0:09:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但因為太堅硬斬不下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.52,0:09:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給在下辦吧\N可能會有危險,你們退後吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.20,0:09:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.95,0:09:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身手不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.80,0:09:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的呢,碰到河水也沒有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.66,0:09:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就如名字一樣\N是不可思議的樹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.16,0:09:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就如我的計算一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.60,0:09:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣\N把他們弄翻到沼裏便完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.17,0:10:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只差少少呢,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.14,0:10:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當你最高興時便幹掉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.80,0:10:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是忍不住呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.51,0:10:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨大漩渦一號,發射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了!飛得太遠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.16,0:10:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛…師傅,沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.07,0:10:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總算是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.94,0:10:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是到底發生了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.20,0:10:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.94,0:10:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但總算到了,快點找萬人草…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.38,0:10:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,不就是那個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.50,0:10:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和婆婆說的形狀\N和顏色也一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.95,0:10:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會有錯了,好\N盡量拿多點回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.55,0:10:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.30,0:11:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏會成為你們的葬身之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你便是古沙也了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.14,0:11:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認識我嗎?那為了答謝你\N便讓你死得沒有痛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.69,0:11:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了,萬人草…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.99,0:11:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟給你避開了呢,小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但今次不會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.20,0:11:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.74,0:11:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.51,0:12:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出來了嗎?不知死活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.21,0:12:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快點把萬人草拿回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.98,0:12:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子便危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.48,0:12:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!\N那麼便速戰速決吧,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.52,0:12:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看招吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算這樣避開嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.93,0:12:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我便來三倍攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.17,0:12:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速度很快,這樣避不開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣了?怎樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.97,0:12:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.04,0:12:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,這裏由我牽制著\N你去找萬人草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.55,0:12:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.02,0:13:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他來了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.65,0:13:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣拉你進沼裏\N把龍神丸溶掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.56,0:13:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.69,0:13:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,快離開他啊,加油!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.30,0:13:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑滋拿號如果咬著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.60,0:13:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便發生什麼事也不會放口的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.03,0:13:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.07,0:13:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想辦法離開他的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.27,0:13:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!沒有辦法嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那個了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.71,0:13:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,用那隻船吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.32,0:13:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸\N用這船打開那傢伙的口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.88,0:13:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.86,0:13:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的東西一會兒便會溶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.57,0:13:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這木是不會這麼容易溶掉的\N龍神丸,再用力吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.31,0:13:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.58,0:14:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手拔出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.02,0:14:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,快浮上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.89,0:14:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.22,0:14:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!來吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力量全開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.61,0:14:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變身!龍王丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.86,0:14:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.67,0:15:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連避的時間也沒有吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.11,0:15:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼便用這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.68,0:15:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.55,0:15:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很麻煩的傢伙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.12,0:15:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些不是普通的蒼蠅啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身體動不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.46,0:15:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛苦吧,痛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.60,0:15:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍王丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.31,0:15:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛吧,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.58,0:15:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變形!鳳凰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.40,0:15:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害!龍王丸可以飛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.39,0:15:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,今次到我們進攻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.14,0:15:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.40,0:16:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.47,0:16:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是鳳雷炮!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳳雷炮嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,再來一次吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.71,0:16:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暫時撤退吧,開始潛航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.01,0:16:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍王丸,不要讓他逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.12,0:16:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去了哪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.69,0:16:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看清楚吧,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.83,0:16:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在了,飛龍拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.41,0:16:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍王丸,拉吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.58,0:16:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.02,0:16:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會給你逃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.22,0:16:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.40,0:16:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是機會了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.43,0:17:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.43,0:17:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,風龍劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輸給了這麼老土的招式呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.15,0:17:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了,對了,師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.64,0:17:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只…只有這個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.10,0:17:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,婆婆,這樣有沒有辦法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.71,0:17:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有完整的萬人草\N便什麼辦法也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,去找醫生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.49,0:18:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那部魔神\N但為何會在這裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰駕駛的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.91,0:18:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.01,0:18:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.52,0:18:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猴…猴子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.12,0:18:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那女孩放下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.82,0:18:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說…說話了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.12,0:18:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要帶這女孩去找醫生\N現在沒空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.66,0:18:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點放下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.20,0:18:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅\N看來照他說話做比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.80,0:18:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作點啊,忍部一族的人\N不會這麼沒出息的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.64,0:19:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅\N猴子好像很清楚火美子的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.38,0:19:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呢,喂!你幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.02,0:19:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給她吃藥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.32,0:19:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!\N你不要給她吃奇怪的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.55,0:19:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底是什麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.32,0:19:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真吵,我的名字叫幻龍齊\N是火美子的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.83,0:19:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個呢…火美子是人類吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.63,0:19:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.33,0:19:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但父親是猴子的話,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.87,0:19:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的祖先也是猴子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.31,0:19:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.81,0:19:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,吃下它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.45,0:19:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子!你醒了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.85,0:19:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,我肚子很餓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.26,0:19:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個呢…火美子,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.23,0:19:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可愛!渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.56,0:19:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要養這猴子,一定要養
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.83,0:20:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子\N不要嚇一跳啊,那猴子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.17,0:20:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.90,0:20:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,那猴子先生\N說是你的父親…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.61,0:20:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是火美子\N我想也不會是她的父親呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.85,0:20:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親!父親!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.59,0:20:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,你長大了呢\N父親你變小了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,這猴子真的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.59,0:20:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,這猴子先生真是你父親嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.36,0:20:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在下不能相信,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.43,0:20:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有和父親一人一半的鏈墜嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.33,0:20:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.14,0:20:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幻龍齊先生你也有\N火美子父親的另一半吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.24,0:20:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是疑心大的河馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.68,0:20:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.15,0:20:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的頭很痛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.89,0:20:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來也平安地父女重聚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.20,0:20:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.19,0:20:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你把萬人沼的古沙也打倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得很好,我要多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.70,0:21:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,婆婆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.63,0:21:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?感覺好像不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.04,0:21:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是百人僊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.34,0:21:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是啊,是千人僊人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.14,0:21:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪個也錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.08,0:21:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是最大的哥哥萬人僊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬人僊人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.62,0:21:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家也是一樣樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.29,0:21:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在這河邊\N一直等救世主很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.72,0:21:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在萬人沼的戰鬥已證明\N你便是真正的救世主了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.70,0:21:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個我送給你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.67,0:21:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼種子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.07,0:21:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,把這太好種子\N種在這第五界層某處的聖地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.81,0:21:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神聖木之上\N便能令這世界恢復原狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.21,0:21:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼神聖木在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.08,0:21:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不知道\N但是你們定能找到出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.49,0:22:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.56,0:22:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.53,0:22:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多惡達是很強的\N你要有心理準備啊

